OL,3,CFormer mining areas still face
OL,4,Cshortage of quality jobs, report finds
OL,6,FMany former coalfield communities
OL,7,Fstill face a shortage of quality jobs
OL,8,F40 years after the miners' strike, a
OL,9,Freport has found.
OL,11,FThe findings from the Sheffield Hallam
OL,12,FUniversity study, 'State of the
OL,13,FCoalfields 2024', commissioned by
OL,14,FCoalfield Regeneration Trust (CRT)
OL,15,Fshow communities face lower pay
OL,16,Fopportunities, poorer health and
OL,17,Fschool performance below the national
OL,18,Faverage.
