OL,3,CFormer mining areas still face
OL,4,Cshortage of quality jobs, report finds
OL,6,FIn total, almost 600,000 coalfield
OL,7,Fresidents, one in six working-age
OL,8,Fadults, claim out-of-work benefits.
OL,10,FProfessor Steve Fothergill, co-author
OL,11,Fof the report, said: "Britain's
OL,12,Fcoalfields have moved on since the job
OL,13,Flosses of the 1980s and '90s. There
OL,14,Fhas been substantial progress in new
OL,15,Fjob creation and the former coalfields
OL,16,Fhave emerged with new roles in local
OL,17,Fand regional economies.
