OL,3,CFormer mining areas still face
OL,4,Cshortage of quality jobs, report finds
OL,6,F"But the full benefits of job growth
OL,7,Fhave not always filtered through to
OL,8,Flocal residents, leaving behind many
OL,9,Fpeople and communities."
OL,11,FThe report also found that if brought
OL,12,Ftogether, the former coalfields would
OL,13,Flikely be the most deprived region in
OL,14,Fthe UK. As a result, the CRT has
OL,15,Fcalled on the government to work with
OL,16,Fthem to help support economic growth
OL,17,Fin the communities.
