OL,3,CFormer mining areas still face
OL,4,Cshortage of quality jobs, report finds
OL,6,FLinda McAvan, Chair of the CRT, said:
OL,7,F"We are seeing positive steps towards
OL,8,Fimproving the economy in the former
OL,9,Fcoalfields ` however it is concerning
OL,10,Fthat our progress is slower than in
OL,11,Fother parts of the country.
OL,13,F"We know that the issues affecting
OL,14,Fcoalfield communities around low-
OL,15,Fquality jobs, lower wages and poor
OL,16,Fhealth can be tackled and the
OL,17,FCoalfields Regeneration Trust is
OL,18,Fplaying its part in addressing these
OL,19,Fissues.
