OL,11,FIn response to the report, a
OL,12,Fspokesperson for the Department for
OL,13,FLevelling Up, Housing and Communities
OL,14,Fsaid: "Coalfield communities are
OL,15,Fbenefitting from levelling up support,
OL,16,Flike the South Yorkshire Mayoral
OL,17,FCombined Authority's long-standing
OL,18,Fdevolution deal, which is providing
OL,19,F#30 million per year for 30 years to
OL,20,Finvest in local priorities.
